headline: Kalshi’s Rise Shakes Up NFL Sunday
summary: Prediction-market startup Kalshi made its name by giving political junkies a way to bet on last year’s presidential election.  Bettors can trade contracts on the outcomes of football, basketball and other games through Kalshi’s app as well as  Robinhood Markets  the brokerage that popularized bets on meme stocks.  Emboldened by a federal judge’s 2024 ruling legalizing election betting, Kalshi introduced sports betting earlier this year.
